3. cs.LG - The paper uses an actor-critic reinforcement learning method, which is a popular approach in deep reinforcement learning and falls under the scope of machine learning.
4. cs.RO - The paper addresses a real-world taxi fleet optimization problem, which falls under the scope of robotics and optimization.
5. cs.SY - The paper deals with a system of multiple agents interacting with each other and the environment, which falls under the scope of control and systems engineering.
